{"word":"King","slug":"king","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>King</b> Called King of Kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=12'>Ezr 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=7'>Eze 26:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=37'>Dan 2:37</a><br/> Divinely authorized<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=15'>Deu 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=9&verse=17'>1Sa 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=12'>1Sa 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=22&verse=10'>1Ch 22:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=12'>2Ch 2:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=8&verse=15'>Pro 8:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=21'>Dan 2:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=2&verse=37'>Dan 2:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=4&verse=17'>Dan 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=20'>Dan 5:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=8&verse=4'>Hos 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=13&verse=11'>Hos 13:11</a><br/> How chosen:<br/> - By divine appointment:<br/> b Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=1'>1Sa 10:1</a><br/> b David and the Davidic dynasty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=13'>1Sa 16:13</a><br/> - Hereditary succession<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=7&verse=16'>2Sa 7:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=30'>1Ki 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=4'>2Ch 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wor